oai_dc:dc.dc:title: List of soldiers in Company E, 4th (Starnes') Tenn. Cav. Regt., CSA
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This 3-page typed list of soldiers in "Company E, Forest's Cavalry" is on stationery from the Farmers Bank of Beech Grove, Tennessee. The men from Coffee, Bedford, and Rutherford counties served in Co. E, 4th (Starnes') Tenn. Cav. Regt., CSA.
